title: Coliseum: Converse x Decibel Collaboration
description: Celebrating their 10th year as one of independent music's most substantive bands, Louisville's Coliseum returned this year with their fourth full-length, the stunning Sister Faith. In the latest Converse X Decibel Collaboration we head to their hometown of Louisville where Ryan Patterson takes us on a tour of his hometown city and discusses the influence it has had both him and his band.
